            A Wedding !&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class="NewsUser">Avrohom 
            - 03-10-2000 at 18:05:50</span> 
            <br>
		  <span class="NewsTitleDescription">Avrohom and Ianenie to make formal vows at the entrance to the Erudin Palace on Odus.</span>
		  </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr bgcolor="#FFFFFF"> 
          <td width="32" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
          <td class="NewsText" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
            <br>
			With great honour and pleasure, let it be known to the world that Lord Avrohom and Lady Ianenie will be holding their formal wedding ceremony on Sunday, Oct 22nd at 10 am CST. The event will consist of pre-ceremony games and gatherings, drinking, and fine comraderie. Following the wedding itself will be a massive fireworks display so bold and bright we aim to wake up the gods themselves!<br><br>Everyone is invited, there will be drinks for all. Avi is sparing no expense as he vows to spend no less than 1kpp on fireworks and drinks.
          </td>
          <td width="16" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">&nbsp;</td>
        </tr>
